        Summary
        Search Deleted files in Recycle bin
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        User should have administrator rights
        Steps
        1. Click on Username on right upper corner of browser window
        2. Click on 'Recycle Bin'
        3. Enter File name
        4. Click on Search icon
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify that Searched file should be present

      • RECOVER_SINGLE_FILE_FROM_RECYCLEBIN_TC

        public void RECOVER_SINGLE_FILE_FROM_RECYCLEBIN_TC()
        Summary
        Recover Single Deleted file from Recycle bin
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        User should have administrator rights
        Steps
        1. Delete File from dashboard
        2. Click on Username on right upper corner of browser window
        3. Click on 'Recycle Bin'
        4. Enter user name
        5. Click on Search icon
        6. Click on 'Recover'
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify that Recovered file should be present on dashboard
